      "span_text": "The 5S rDNA units of A. belladonna were amplified by PCR using genomic DNA isolated from leaves of 3month-old plants by DNeasy Plant kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA), Pfu DNA polymerase (Thermo Fisher Scientific, Inc.) and primers Pr5S-L (5′-CAATGCGGCCGCGAG AGTAGTACTAGGATGCGTGAC-3′) + Pr5S-R (5′-CAT TGCGGCCGCTTAACTTCGGAGTTCTGATGGGA-3′) complimentary to the 5S rRNA coding region [CITATION_1] were used for amplification."
